data.description: SELLR SAYS SELL!! Beautifully renovated 3 bedroom 2 bathroom single family home with laminate wood floors throughout, newer appliances, stylish barn doors, tankless water heater, new AC, and nice details with lovely finishes. Washer/dryer, and nice sized backyard with shed and mango trees. Great income producing home, as rents soar on Single Family Homes, or the perfect first or second home that will appreciate nicely from an area growing with new residential and commercial developments around the corner. Seconds from I-95, Gulfstream Casino and shops, Aventura Mall, and only five minutes to the beach. Be the lucky ones on the block to own this fully gated property off Hallandale Beach Blvd. This home is definitely the gem of the neighborhood. MUST SEE!!! ***Seller must sell!!***
